Wedd., Chlor. Andina 1: 108. 1856. Type: Peru. Cusco: dept. de Cuzco, Oct 1839-Feb 1840, C. Gay 1870 (lectotype, designated here: P [P01816797]), syn. nov.
</paragraph>
